To run locally (inside docs dir):
jekyll serve --host=0.0.0.0 --config _config.yml

For watermark (GimP):
1) open the image on which watermark needs to be added
2) file-> open as layer  -> (select your logo (images/watermark))
3) Resize the logo
    (right bottom side find the logo)
    right click -> scale layer -> 250 x 52
4) Position the logo to the desired logo
5) Make it transparent
    make opacity to 5